    "Following the convolutional blocks, the feature maps from all branches are flattened and concatenated, creating a unified representation of the input data.",
    "This representation is passed through several fully connected layers, culminating in a sigmoid activation for binary classification.",
    "During branching, the branched input goes through individual models.",
    "The model extracts information from each of the branches and concatenates them.",
    "As each branch focuses on a specific HU-intensity range, the data extraction is more effective, and the model can classify the tumor more efficiently."
